These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
House: art-deco, townhouse, palace, gothic-revival
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the townhouse house##2
4. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
5. the palace house is between the townhouse house and the art-deco house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| House   | gothic-revival         | townhouse   | palace | art-deco       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
4 different pets are kept: lizard, chinchilla, bird, dog
1. the owner of the dog is between the person who's hobby is reading and the owner of the chinchilla##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Pet   | chinchilla    | dog   | lizard | bird       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, corn, cranberry, kale
4 different games are played: go, mah-jongg, backgammon, chess
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person eating kale##1
2. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person eating corn##2
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1
4. the person playing chess is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person eating corn is the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Game   | mah-jongg | backgammon   | chess | go |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, tram, skateboard, train
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, rugby, tennis
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person driving the train##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Transport     | train   | jet-ski    | skateboard       | tram   |
| Sport   | rugby | tennis | basketball | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, soy-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, documentary, adventure, epic
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching documentary movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta        | iced-tea | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre      | adventure | documentary  | epic | horror    |

