.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, house, punk
City: colone, hannover, paris, london
1. the fan of gospel is the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
5. the fan of electronic is between the person traveling to colone and the fan of house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | gospel | electronic | house      |
| City     | paris | colone    | hannover  | london |

