.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, soccer, weightlifting
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, dubstep, funk, trance
1. the fan of folk is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the fan of dubstep is between the person who's sport is soccer and the fan of funk##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
4. the fan of folk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | biathlon | weightlifting | soccer     | lacrosse   |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | dubstep     | trance | folk |

