.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, soul, rock, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of soul##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the fan of soul and the person who's sport is tennis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre    | trance   | rock      | soul   | house  |
| Sport   | tennis | ice-hockey | swimming | baseball |

