2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person watching sports movies and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
