.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-14::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, march, october
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, martial-arts, spy
1. the person who's birthday is in april is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching epic movies##2
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Birthday           | february | october | march | april |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | animation | spy         | martial-arts |

