.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, french, japanese
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, baccarat, dunhill, swisher
1. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the japanese is the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the french is between the dunhill-smoker and the dutch##2
4. the japanese is on the right of the french##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | american | dutch | french | japanese |
| Cigar     | vegafina     | baccarat   | swisher | dunhill  |

