3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
