.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, radish, cauliflower, mango
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person eating mango is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating cauliflower##2
5. the person eating cauliflower is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food   | mango   | artichoke   | radish | cauliflower |
| Sport         | baseball | basketball | rowing     | golf    |

