.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, singing, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, western, epic, fantasy
1. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person watching documentary movies and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | singing    | sudoku     | card-games | dancing |
| Movie-Genre     | western | fantasy | epic       | documentary     |

 